<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Shipped</title>
    <style>
        /* Add your CSS styles for the email here */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .order {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .order-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .order-details {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .order-items {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .item-image {
            max-width: 100px;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    Dear Customer, 
    <br />
    <p>This email is to confirm that your order has been shipped.</p>
    <br/>
        <% const store=data[storeId]; %>
            <div class="order"></div>
                <div class="order-details">
                        <p><strong>Order ID:</strong>
                            <%= order.orderId %>
                        </p>
                        <p><strong>Order Date:</strong>
                            <%= order.orderDate %>
                        </p>
                        <p><strong>Order Amount:</strong>
                            <%= order.orderAmount %>
                        </p>
                </div>
                <div class="order-items">
                        <% order.items.forEach(item=> { %>
                        <div class="item">
                            <div class="item-image">
                                <img style="height: 50px; width: 50px;" src="<%= item.thumbnail %>"
                                        alt="<%= item.title %>">
                            </div>
                            <div class="item-details">
                                    <p><strong>Product:</strong>
                                        <%= item.title %>
                                    </p>
                                    <p><strong>Quantity:</strong>
                                        <%= item.quantity %>
                                    </p>
                                    <p><strong>Unit Price:</strong>
                                        <%= item.unit_price %>
                                    </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                     <% }); %>
                </div>
            </div>
                <br />
                <p>Please note that if you wish to review your order details or receipt, you may do so by visiting the 'My Orders' section on our website.</p>
                <p>If you did not place this order, please reach out to our customer support immediately at <a href='mailto:support@hamzamarket.com'>support@hamzamarket.com.</a></p>
                <p>We truly appreciate your business with Hamza and look forward to serving you again.</p>
                <br/>
                Best regards, <br />
                The Hamza Team<br />

